where CB and CT represent the SiO2 and electrolyte interfacial capacitances, respectively. Assuming a constant pH and fully depleted channel at VTG = VTH, which implies neither change in CT nor more charge accumulation, the net charge difference becomes zero33. Therefore, the VTH value is given by,3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
